text: The opportunity you've been waiting for is here! Build your dream home on this water view property nestled within the Horizon community near Semiahmoo resort & country club. Have the best of both worlds by creating a home tailored to your needs while enjoying your peaceful living spaces within a vibrant community. This privately gated neighborhood includes walking trails, Boche ball courts, horseshoe pits w/ a future park coming soon. Bring your own plans, create your own plans, or bring your own builder to make this piece of property come to life & design your forever home. Dont have a builder? No problem, as Noffke Homes can offer assistance in building your custom home upon request.

Rare opportunity to own a true 2 bedroom condominium at the Snowater resort; comes fully furnished. Located on the Nooksack River adjacent to the Mt. Baker Snoqualmie National Forest. Easy access to year-round outdoor recreation at Mt. Baker Ski Area and the backcountry. The resort grounds include tennis, pickleball, basketball, racquetball courts, 2 indoor swimming pools, jacuzzi, sauna, and gym. Cook out at the riverfront community BBQ and picnic area or enjoy the quiet at the historical log cabin. Trails surround the property. The perfect place for relaxation and recreation in every season. Capital improvements recently completed: New roof, completed chimney chase & painting project, new screen doors. No special assessment anticipated.

Cozy and welcoming 2 bedroom 1 bath wood and stone Chalet-style home on over an acre in Maple Falls. The home features wood floors, vaulted ceilings, an updated kitchen and an extra room for entertaining upstairs. With over an acre of property, including a fenced yard, shop space and additional outbuildings, theres room for all your hobbies. The 2 bay garage has a bonus room as well. Enjoy views of the foothills plus proximity to Mount Baker and the great outdoors. This turn-key home is ready for it's next owner!

FANTASTIC INVESTOR OPPORTUNITY!Open floor-plan with spacious rooms and ample storage throughout. Potential for a 4th bedroom on the lower level, plus an extra unfinished area for added flexibility. Amazing potential with this rare gem! Dont miss out on all the fantastic Sudden Valley amenities!

Coveted, south-facing waterfront location at Sandy Point Shores w/ spectacular Mt Baker & Island views! Amazing kitchen, large island, walk-in pantry, custom cabs, granite, SS appls. Cozy FP in Living Room, Office w/ built-ins +wall bed, bath nearby. Upstairs Primary Suite w/ walk-in shower & closet, and the view: WOW! Two more beds, hall bath + laundry. Garage new in 2021 w/ huge Family Room above, includes bath, kitchenette counter, sink, cabs, & fridge that could be Mother-in-Law Suite, home gym, hobby room, play area! Large patio on the waterfront is a great place to entertain or relax with friends. Go crabbing, fishing, kayaking, San Juan Island cruising! Marina, Golf, Tennis, Play Areas. Come live the ultimate coastal lifestyle!
nearby_schools: Ferndale School District, Lummi High School, Lummi Elementary School

text: Tucked away in a quiet neighborhood, this charming 3-bedroom, 1.75-bath home offers privacy and comfort. The large backyard, bordered by a serene forest, and a deck off the dining room, provide peaceful outdoor space. Inside, the open-concept layout fills the home with natural light, creating an inviting atmosphere perfect for entertaining. Enjoy recent updates including new paint, solid-core interior doors, modern fixtures, white shaker cabinetry, quartz countertops, new carpet, and LVP flooring. Featuring gas and wood burning fireplaces for added warmth. The spacious primary bedroom features an ensuite bath. Just minutes to downtown shopping and dining, this home combines seclusion with convenience. Dont miss out on this lovely retreat!

Have you ever dreamed of having hiking or mountain biking trails just outside your door? Or just want to get away from it all ? This very private home on 18+ acres offers just that! It needs some TLC to really shine again but you will see how much love went into its construction. Gorgeous tongue and groove ceilings, exposed beams, six panel doors and a stunning formal dining room that would make a great sun room, studio, office or second living area. Main level living plus two bedrooms and a bathroom upstairs. A pre-inspection was conducted & many repairs were made already including new luxury vinyl plank flooring on the main floor & part of the upstairs. The acreage could be divided for a second home. Very remote with endless potential!

RARE double-parcel private estate in the heart of Bellingham just minutes to shopping, Downtown, and I-5. Pacific Northwest JEWEL on expansive half-acre, park-like, DOUBLE LOT in the heart of Bellingham. Architected landscaping elevates outdoor entertaining. Attention to detail and craftsmanship shows in inlaid hardwood floors and the custom cherry kitchen. Formal Living, Dining, and private office spaces exude elegance with curved walls of windows. Enjoy stunning sunsets over the City and Bellingham Bay from the Great Room and expansive west-facing deck. Zero-step entry and a main-level primary suite ensures ease of living. Stay active in the well-equipped home gym. Trailhead across the street offers endless outdoor exploration.

Discover the brand-new 2-story floor plan at The Ridge in Blaine, offered for the first time! This home boasts a primary bedroom on the main floor for easy living and convenience. With 4 bedrooms in total, one can be used as a home office on the main level. The second story offers a versatile bonus loft area. Designed with comfort and style, this home includes luxury vinyl plank flooring, quartz countertops, and modern finishes throughout. The open & bright floorplan and flexible layout make this home perfect for any lifestyle. Conveniently located near downtown Blaine and I-5 for easy access to all amenities. $5, 000 Buyer Credit available with our preferred lender, Becky Farrar at Evergreen Home Loans. Don't miss this amazing opportunity!

This charming classic 3 bedroom 1 1/2 bath home is well cared for throughout the years. Located in established neighborhood on dead end street. The heated shop has 2 car garage door and plenty of work space. A warm welcome greets you with beautiful brick fireplace and cozy sitting area off the kitchen. Kitchen well equipped with stainless frig, newer dishwasher and plenty of space to cook, bake and enjoy meals. The living area is spacious enough to house grand piano accented by large picture window with partial view of Bellingham Bay. Many delightful dinners are served in the dining area. The utility rm provides access to outdoor courtyard. A large corner lot with fenced back yard is nicely maintained. Fruit trees, garden and play area!
nearby_schools: Northwest Educational Service District 189, Bellingham Public Schools

text: Tucked away at the end of a quiet cul de sac, fantastic location walking distance to Barkley Village! Fully updated and lives like new, this 4 bedroom townhome will not disappoint! Open concept living on the main floor with 4 bedrooms upstairs including a primary suite with a private balcony. Everything inside is brand new including LVP flooring and carpet, doors and trim, white shaker cabinetry, quartz countertops, stainless appliances, LED lighting, and fresh paint. Oversized 2 car garage with brand new garage door and this home abuts the famous Bellingham interurban trail system!

Welcome to Hannah Creek! This neighborhood in Bellingham is right next to miles of hiking and biking trails on Galbraith Mountain. Enter to see the spacious living room and open kitchen with a big island. A deck looks over the backyard and greenbelt with a small creek. Upstairs has a spacious primary bedroom, and 2 other bedrooms plus a convenient utility room. Downstairs is a spacious rec room and a roughed in bathroom, with access to the patio and fully fenced backyard, perfect for your dog. The home has cozy radiant floor heat throughout, with different temperature zones you can control. You can be hiking trails, or downtown, in 10 minutes! New roof in 2023. Don't miss this one!

This exquisitely cared-for Geneva Neighborhood 2-story home features a graceful design & spacious layout. Enter the expansive living room, where vaulted ceilings & over-height windows w/plantation shutters & drapes create an elegant atmosphere. The open-concept dining area & gourmet kitchen are perfect for entertaining. Primary suite w/remodeled bath & walk-in are on the main floor, along w/ laundry & a powder room. Upstairs, are 2 large guest BR's, a large Bonus Room w/closet & remodeled 3/4 bath. The back deck & covered entertaining area are magazine-cover worthy, leaving the rest of the large, fenced back yard for gardening, games & gatherings! Extras include an instant-on backup generator, a large 2-car garage + a garden shed!

This spacious 4-bed, 2-bath home is situated on almost a half-acre lot in the desirable Happy Valley neighborhood on the Southside of Bellingham. Just a stones throw from Joes Garden and Western Washington University, this property offers convenience and potential. The home features a fully fenced backyard and paid off solar panels(36-LG ACe 375-watt) black-framed modules worth over $32, 000, installed in 2021. With all living spaces on one level, its ideal for a variety of lifestyles. Investor alertthis property is being sold as-is, offering a fantastic opportunity to renovate or customize to your liking. According to City of Bellingham, 2 ADUs (either attached or detached) could be added. Prime location with endless possibilities!

This is a gem of an investment property right in the heart of Fairhaven in the Urban Village! Live in the main 3 bed house and get a great interest rate, and then rent the two upper 2 bedroom units. All the character is intact with crown molding, white shaker cabinets, built-ins and each room is very generously sized. The upper 2 units have access from an exterior stairway off the back side of the triplex. There is a basement that has a work shop and storage units, along with coin-op washer and dryer (for the upper units, but they are W/D ready, too) and a 3/4 bath that is about .75% done, and additional units could be added down there. Electrical, plumbing, furnaces and hot water were updated in 2000 or sooner.
